                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" class="text-left">
                        <span>備註欄：</span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="4">
                        <span class="display: block;"></span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="2" class="text-left">
                        <span>經收人：</span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="4">
                        <span class="display: block;"></span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="6" rowspan="2" class="align-middle">
                        <span>
                            池上多力米股份有限公司
                            <br />
                            /建興碾米工廠
                        </span>
                    </td>
                    <td colspan="6" class="text-left">
                        <span>台東縣池上鄉中山路193-1號1樓</span>
                    </td>
